Weapons Guidelines:

1. No weapons above weapon class of 18.
   (without approval from a senior wiz)
2. No returns greater than 7.
   (without approval from a senior wiz)
3. The % of the return should be no greater
   than 30%.
   (without approval from a senior wiz)

To get approval from a senior wiz to stray
from these guidelines. You must present a
feesible deterent for the weapon, ie. spell
point or hit point loss.
